The famous Scott Peterson derailed using the past while claiming that his murdered woman was alive, triggering a national search to find her.
Deceiver individuals can also use a distant language: "I have not had sexual relations with this woman... Miss Lewinsky" or repeat a completely difficult question.
The most common verbal indicators are subtle.
Someone can use a lot of "wood language" when answering a difficult question: "Well... to tell you the truth... if I remember well... to my knowledge."
