We really look forward to producing it.
We love this country, we love surfing and jungle; for both things, Costa Rica is one of the best countries in the world.
How did you discover Costa Rica and its waves to surf?
We have many friends surfers and I have a very good friend who lives in Tamarindo and the waves are incredible there.
